{"word":"κατασπείρω","slug":"κατασπείρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατασπείρω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-σπερῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to sow thickly</i>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἀνίας κ.</el> <i>to sow a crop</i> of sorrows, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to beget</i>, <el>τέκνα</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to scatter over</i>, as in sowing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to besprinkle</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}